###########################################################
# Automated iOS project deploy script for TestFlightApp.com
# https://github.com/mishakarpenko/testflightappdeploy
# http://mishakarpenko.com
###########################################################

Script written in bash. Feel free to send me your propositions and improvements.
Will be useful to launch right after your VCS commit or push.

How to use
----------
1. First copy testflightappdeploy.sh file into your projects directory (near your *.xcodeproj file), and edit it entering your Apple Developer credentials, TestFlight API tokens and stuff.
2. Make testflightappdeploy.sh executable: chmod +x testflightappdeploy.sh
3. That's all, run ./testflightappdeploy.sh from your project directory.